text: The 2016 Coupe Banque Nationale was a tennis tournament played on indoor carpet courts. It was the 24th edition of the Tournoi de Québec and part of the WTA International tournaments of the 2016 WTA Tour. It took place at the PEPS de l'Université Laval in Quebec City, Canada, from September 12 through September 18, 2016. ==Points and prize money== ===Point distribution=== {|class=wikitable
